provocative interviews and speeches in different provinces and
appointing inexperienced people to managerial posts at the
interior ministry.
</P>
<P>
According to the Majlis regulations, Nouri should appear
before the Majlis within 10 days to give his explanation after
the proposed motion for the impeachment was submitted to the
Majlis.
</P>
<P>
The proposed motion against Nouri was believed to be another
step launched by the conservatives against the moderate
government of President Khatami, following their efforts to put
Tehran Mayor Gholamhussein Karbaschi, Khatami's another strong
supporter, on trial on corrupt charges. 
