<TEXT>
<P>
ADDIS ABABA, June 10 (Xinhua) -- The Ethiopian Chamber of
Commerce said Wednesday that the business community is ready to
facilitate the transportation of goods from the port of Djibouti
to the hinterland.
</P>
<P>
According to the Ethiopian News Agency, president of the
chamber Kebour Genna said efforts are being made to put in place
a rapid transit system.
</P>
<P>
