to propose a "phase of persuasion" during which Russia will help
negotiate with the Yugoslav federation and the ethnic Albanians in
Kosovo.
</P>
<P>
Milosevic's Moscow visit next week is apparently part of
Russia's efforts to broker a peaceful solution to the crisis in
the "phase of persuasion." 
