mainland tourists a chance to visit the Hong Kong Special
Administration Region.
</P>
<P>
This is the fourth officially authorized Hong Kong tour in
China, after those provided by China Travel Service, Guangdong
China Travel Service, and Fujian Huamin Travel Service.
</P>
<P>
