arrange a series of colorful Hongkong tours for mainland tourists.
</P>
<P>
The mainland provides the largest source of tourists for Hong
Kong. On May 29, the HKSAR government announced that it will
increase the daily quota for mainland tourists to 1,500, from
1,142, as of July 1. 
