vessel, frigate and patrol boat, and a Venezuelan submarine based
at La Guaria harbor, north of Caracas.
</P>
<P>
The joint naval exercise has been carried out twice a year for
15 years, and is part of an agreement between both governments to
consolidate operations between their forces. 
