<TEXT>
<P>
LIMA, June 10 (Xinhua) -- The inauguration of the World Cup
finals "France 98" was followed today by television by thousand of
Peruvians, in spite of their team not participating in this
world tournament which will last until July 12.
</P>
<P>
The district municipality of Miraflores, in the limits of this
city has installed two giant screens at the municipal sports
complex so that the fans may watch the matches.
</P>
<P>
Since this morning, elementary and high school students arrived
with their tutors to watch the matches as well as workers and all
kind of public.
</P>
<P>
However, the expectative has not resulted unrestrainable,
commerces, study centers and companies have worked normally during
the initial match Scotland-Brazil.
</P>
<P>
According to information provided by the local media, the
soccer fans declared that a championship without their national
soccer team cannot be the same, but that they will follow the
matches anyway.
</P>
<P>
In every corner of Peru and during the 33 days of this
tournament, there will be a T.V. set that transmits the victories
and hardships of 704 players, 34 arbiters and 32 coaches who will
gather in 10 French stadiums to take part in the 64 matches of the
program. 
