<HEADLINE> Romania Sends Policemen in Bosnia-Herzegovina </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BUCHAREST, June 10 (Xinhua) -- The parliament of Romania
approved Wednesday Romania's participation in the Police
International Group in Bosnia-Hertegovina.
</P>
<P>
The Senate and the Chamber of Deputies made the move in a joint
sitting at the request of President Emil Constantinescu.
</P>
<P>
