<HEADLINE> Norway, Morocco Draw 2-2 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>

<P>
MONTPELLIER, June 10 (XInhua) -- Norway rallied to draw Morocco
2-2 in a World Cup Group A match here on Wednesday.
